contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentLabel: Setting Up a Solution for Integrating Custom Code in Xperience by Kentico on macOS
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentShortDescription: Kentico community member and Xperience by Kentico enthusiast Milan Lund prefers to build Xperience by Kentico solutions on his Apple Macbook using VS Code. If that sounds interesting to you, read his full step-by-step post where he covers everything you need to know!
